The paper discusses the use of deep learning neural networks for cancer variant calling, which is a common application of machine learning in the field of bioinformatics. The paper specifically focuses on the use of deep Bayesian recurrent neural networks, which are a type of neural network commonly used in natural language processing and time series analysis. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
